  "texts": [
    "As we did above, we will consider light and heavy fields separately.Light fields.",
    "First consider light fields, i.e.",
    "those in the complementary series, and the modes with n = |h| where the solution to the homogeneous equation of motion is given by (2.39).",
    "Given that this solution involves a single Hankel function, the properties of G h |h|,S (η 1, η 2, k) will be very similar to what we encountered in the CCM case but with κ = 0.",
    "Indeed, for light fields we therefore already know that this propagator is purely real after Wick rotation."
